vote.title: Authorize City nomination of Village Practice Management Company, LLC (“VillageMD”) proposed project, with 10152 Lake June Road as the main qualified site, to receive designation as an Enterprise Zone Project under the Texas Enterprise Zone Act, as amended (Texas Government Code, Chapter 2303) to the Office of the Governor, Economic Development and Tourism division, through the Economic Development Bank - Financing: No cost consideration to the City
